info.description: Crispy Mediterranean falafels on a base of protein-rich quinoa and fresh greens. Topped with pinto beans, zesty corn salsa, homemade pico-de-gallo, and sautéed fajita vegetables. Finished with our spicy signature Coastal Pachadi, crema de yogurt and a drizzle of lemon-tahini dressing.
